{"tid":1312692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水癲狗打人 原來又係陶輝做指揮官","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T00:50:28.000Z","uid":176442,"like":42,"dislike":528,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"8352a15a59c704f06f1cfacb1b32bb5ea963dfc8","tid":1312692,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190713&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59820825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190713%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59820825&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f3147649\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190713%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59820825&h=49c19a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190713&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59820825</a>  <br />\n<br />\n【光復上水】3千警力清場 指揮官陶輝再現<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上在上水清場，被指在6.12金鐘警民衝突中，有份決定施放150枚催淚彈、橡膠子彈及布袋彈的英籍總警司陶輝（Rupert Dover），再次現身港鐵上水站外。消息稱，今次清場行動警方派出3隊應變大隊，警力達3千人，下午的警民衝突由新界北應變大隊負責清場，而晚上的大清場行動則由西九龍應變大隊及新界北應變大隊負責展開，兩隊的指揮官分別為總警司周一鳴及陶輝。<br />\n<br />\n早前灣仔警察總部被包圍事件中，陶輝率領警員出動驅散示威者，大批記者再追問他警方於6.12衝突中有否使用過份武力，以及是否由他決定向示威者施放催淚彈，他沒有回答記者提問，由同袍護送離開。"},{"pid":"8abf3b8d6402e29a5230b1ea7d2af256ea3eb148","tid":1312692,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"打沙包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ab300bff0080339b4c829ed9047bc3c2ae528b","tid":1312692,"uid":11001,"like":246,"dislike":0,"score":246,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"又係外國勢力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debbd0253f09aabe6b70ba2942598b7b3d4e0781","tid":1312692,"uid":176442,"like":479,"dislike":1,"score":478,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"呢條死黑警有暴力傾向<br />\n但係仍然有得做指揮官<br />\n代表咩？"},{"pid":"0aa17ca9439aee2c1322cf1f07977